<% title = 'LDGsCORD'; %>
<section>
    <div id="app">
        <div id="channels">
            <button id="dmButton" class="round-button">DM</button>
        </div>
        <div id="channel-container">
            <button class="round-button">DM</button> 
        </div>
    
        <div id="myModal" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close">&times;</span>
                <h2>서버를 만들어보세요</h2>
                <p>서버는 나와 친구들이 함께 어울리는 공간입니다. 내 서버를 만들고 대화를 시작해보세요.</p>
                <div class="mini-btn-container">
                    <form action="/channels/create" method="post">
                        <input type="text" name="servername" placeholder="My Server" required>
                        <button id="actionButton" class="rect-button" type="submit">직접 만들기</button>
                    </form>
                    <p>템플릿으로 시작</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script src="/public/js/channels.js"></script>
</section>